1
00:00:06,082 --> 00:00:08,593
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,593 --> 00:00:12,162
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,162 --> 00:00:18,155
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,155 --> 00:00:24,481
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,481 --> 00:00:30,702
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,702 --> 00:00:35,988
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:35,988 --> 00:00:43,088
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,088 --> 00:00:48,312
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,312 --> 00:00:49,925
♫ Be your light ♫

10
00:00:49,925 --> 00:00:55,588
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,588 --> 00:01:02,088
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,088 --> 00:01:08,555
♫ With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,555 --> 00:01:11,920
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:12,602 --> 00:01:16,859
He came all the way here. Aren't you a bit too mean to him?

15
00:01:16,859 --> 00:01:20,780
Ye Xiaowen, what's going on? Why did you call for backup?

16
00:01:21,339 --> 00:01:22,840
What do you mean call for backup?

17
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:25,425
Didn't you tell your friend to lock Brother Zhe in the equipment room?

18
00:01:25,425 --> 00:01:31,059
Hurry up. Hurry up and release him. If Coach finds out, we'll all be dismissed.

19
00:01:46,414 --> 00:01:49,359
You said Ye Xiaowen gave up the first place to save you?

20
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:52,599
Yes, of course. Let me tell you,

21
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:55,584
I'm still recovering from a wound right here.

22
00:01:55,584 --> 00:01:57,284
Oh my.

23
00:01:57,284 --> 00:02:00,300
How could someone like him be a snitch?

24
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,740
No.

25
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:04,699
If you say Ye Xiaowen didn't tell on us, then bring out the evidence to prove it.

26
00:02:04,699 --> 00:02:07,080
If it wasn't him, how did Coach Zhang find out?

27
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:08,900
Can't you just go and ask the coach?

28
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:11,400
Ask the coach? I wouldn't dare.

29
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:14,300
Why were you so brave when you smacked your head with this just now?

30
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:16,319
Where's your courage now?

31
00:02:17,219 --> 00:02:18,419
- Gao Yang!
- Brother Zhe!

32
00:02:18,419 --> 00:02:19,560
- Gao Yang!
- Brother Zhe!

33
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,879
- Brother Zhe!
- Coming. Coming.

34
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,379
Gao Yang!

35
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,280
What's up?

36
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:30,840
Didn't I tell you to leave? Why did you come back?

37
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,660
I'm just having a chat with Zhezhe.

38
00:02:34,939 --> 00:02:36,959
I'm having a chat with Brother Yang.

39
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:42,339
You really can't do anything without me.

40
00:02:42,339 --> 00:02:45,479
Take this, the discus.

41
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,399
Where are you going?

42
00:02:52,930 --> 00:02:53,939
Are you okay?

43
00:02:53,939 --> 00:02:55,739
I'm fine.

44
00:02:58,650 --> 00:03:02,099
You... are a parent?

45
00:03:04,900 --> 00:03:06,800
Yes.

46
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,460
I'm Ye Xiaowen's elder brother.

47
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:11,460
Well, I came to see him on behalf of the family.

48
00:03:11,460 --> 00:03:15,760
Xiaowen has never been far from home.

49
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,140
Everyone in the family is worried about him.

50
00:03:17,140 --> 00:03:20,840
Gao Yang, Brother Bin's son?

51
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:23,199
What's there to worry about?

52
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:26,740
I noticed that your walls here are a bit short.

53
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:30,180
If a bad guy climbs over the wall at night, it's very dangerous.

54
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:32,939
That's not possible. We have surveillance cameras around here.

55
00:03:32,939 --> 00:03:35,240
Tell your dad to relax.

56
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,779
Oh, there are surveillance cameras here?

57
00:03:37,779 --> 00:03:39,839
That's a great relief.

58
00:03:39,839 --> 00:03:41,159
Coach Zhang,

59
00:03:41,159 --> 00:03:44,860
you have to pay more attention to our Xiaowen. Our entire family really cares about him.

60
00:03:44,860 --> 00:03:46,099
Don't worry.

61
00:03:46,099 --> 00:03:49,199
Thank you. And Mi Jia too.

62
00:03:49,199 --> 00:03:51,639
What did I tell you? People need to communicate.

63
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:54,139
The sooner you communicate, the sooner you solve a problem. You have to use your brain.

64
00:03:54,139 --> 00:03:55,740
Xiaowen.

65
00:03:56,219 --> 00:03:57,919
Well...

66
00:03:58,300 --> 00:03:59,800
I'm sorry.

67
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,659
Let's do it together.

68
00:04:02,659 --> 00:04:04,240
I'm sorry!

69
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,539
It's okay. It's good to clear up the misunderstanding.

70
00:04:06,539 --> 00:04:09,619
What I've done recently was indeed not very kind.

71
00:04:09,619 --> 00:04:13,840
How about this? I'll treat you to dinner tonight as my apology.

72
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,300
No, thank you.

73
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:16,859
No, you have to go.

74
00:04:16,859 --> 00:04:19,020
Exactly. Give Zhezhe some respect, all right?

75
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:23,319
Listen to Brother Yang. You have to come tonight. I'll go and take care of the wound.

76
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:24,841
It's settled then.

77
00:04:24,841 --> 00:04:26,966
- I'll see you in a bit.
- It's settled.

78
00:04:26,966 --> 00:04:29,318
What time is your train tonight? Can you make it?

79
00:04:29,318 --> 00:04:31,140
It's 8 o'clock. I'm sure I can make it.

80
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:34,919
Let's go. Mi Jia, let's go enjoy the feast.

81
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:41,707
G-Gao Yang made a huge contribution this time. You should really thank him.

82
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:51,212
[Episode 20: Returning To the Past]

83
00:04:55,850 --> 00:04:57,419
Come on.

84
00:04:57,419 --> 00:05:00,480
These are the best stir-fries in our cafeteria.

85
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:03,419
Starting eating. Eat as much as you want. Go ahead, there's more.

86
00:05:03,419 --> 00:05:05,600
Hurry up and eat, Mi Jia.

87
00:05:06,339 --> 00:05:09,140
Hurry up and eat. After dinner, go to the train station.

88
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:13,000
What's the hurry? It's only 6 p.m. now. My train departs at 8 p.m.

89
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,800
It's still early.

90
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:18,120
Where's your ticket? Let me check it again.

91
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,840
Such a nag.

92
00:05:25,530 --> 00:05:27,999
Here, check it. Check it carefully.

93
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:33,879
When did you say the train departs?

94
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:35,579
8 p.m.

95
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:39,280
This is not bad, Mi Jia.

96
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:41,260
Look at it again.

97
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:45,339
Look at what? Isn't it written here? 18:00.

98
00:05:53,210 --> 00:05:56,859
I saw it wrong. I'll buy a ticket for the next train.

99
00:05:57,460 --> 00:06:01,299
There's only one train to Tieyuan per day. Where will you go and buy it?

100
00:06:01,299 --> 00:06:02,580
I'll buy the ticket for tomorrow then.

101
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:05,020
What about tonight? Where are you going to sleep tonight?

102
00:06:05,020 --> 00:06:07,359
I'll go find an internet café for the night.

103
00:06:07,359 --> 00:06:10,239
Hurry up and eat. It's not a big deal, right?

104
00:06:10,239 --> 00:06:13,640
You have to stay calm, you know? Play it by ear.

105
00:06:16,410 --> 00:06:18,380
Stay in my dorm tonight.

106
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:24,400
Y-You can't, Xiaowen. Wh-what if Coach finds out and p-punishes you?

107
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:27,140
It's okay. Brother Yang, stay here.

108
00:06:27,140 --> 00:06:29,840
I'll take responsibility for any consequences.

109
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:33,140
This fish is really tasty. There's more.

110
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:35,200
Fine, you take responsibility.

111
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:37,840
He'll take responsibility. Just eat.

112
00:06:43,179 --> 00:06:48,240
You two eat first. I'll go call Mr. Gao and let him know.

113
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,999
Come back soon.

114
00:06:49,999 --> 00:06:52,760
Come on, Mi Jia, have some fish.

115
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:58,339
Double Aces.

116
00:07:03,170 --> 00:07:05,099
Double twos.

117
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:07,560
You can't beat that, right?

118
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:10,260
It's so big. How many cards do you have left?

119
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:11,959
Just one.

120
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,899
Come on, Brother Yang.

121
00:07:13,899 --> 00:07:15,520
Come on. Come on.

122
00:07:19,850 --> 00:07:22,239
That's unfortunate. A rocket.

123
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:27,779
Stick it on. That's too bad. Come on.

124
00:07:27,779 --> 00:07:30,620
- He has two Jokers every time.
- Hurry up and stick it on.

125
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:34,620
Brother Yang, you're so good at playing cards. Why don't you stay for a few more days?

126
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:38,039
No, no, I have to go home tomorrow.

127
00:07:40,410 --> 00:07:44,600
That's enough. Don't affect their training tomorrow.

128
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:47,539
He won't affect us. Xiaowen, come and play a few rounds.

129
00:07:47,539 --> 00:07:49,239
I'm not playing.

130
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:54,099
Well, deal the cards first.

131
00:08:05,310 --> 00:08:06,919
Check this out.

132
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:11,300
I can accept your compliment.

133
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:16,160
Brother Yang, you are quite fond of learning. You even brought study materials on a trip.

134
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:20,239
I can't help it. I'm good at everything. I'm good at studying and playing cards.

135
00:08:20,239 --> 00:08:23,099
We have to go to bed after this round. You still have to train tomorrow.

136
00:08:23,099 --> 00:08:24,699
Okay.

137
00:08:25,539 --> 00:08:28,400
Lights out! Hurry up and go to sleep!

138
00:09:03,930 --> 00:09:06,780
Hurry up and go to sleep. Stop playing cards.

139
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,559
- Yes, Coach.
- Yes, Coach.

140
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:15,419
Brother Yang. Brother Yang.

141
00:09:15,419 --> 00:09:17,479
He left. Come on.

142
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:21,079
He scared me to death. Good thing I was clever.

143
00:09:21,079 --> 00:09:22,900
Let's continue. Who called out he's the Landlord just now? (Dou dizhu, popular card game in China)

144
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:23,960
- Me, me.
- Him.

145
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,539
Alright, come on.

146
00:09:25,539 --> 00:09:27,039
The landlord has pretty good cards.

147
00:09:27,039 --> 00:09:28,539
Of course.

148
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:48,799
Four twos, can't beat that.

149
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:50,317
Time to wake up.

150
00:09:50,317 --> 00:09:51,279
Four twos, can't beat that.

151
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:52,980
The sun is shining on your buttocks (late morning, sleeping in).

152
00:09:52,980 --> 00:09:56,200
No, you play your cards.

153
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:06,620
Did you sleep well?

154
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,520
Why am I here?

155
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:18,980
Not bad, Gao Yang. You're not a picky sleeper.

156
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:21,219
Are you treating my place here like a hotel?

157
00:10:21,219 --> 00:10:22,820
No, no.

158
00:10:25,930 --> 00:10:31,159
I don't let you go out to have fun so you snuck a person in here?

159
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:35,659
I told you about the consequences of violating the rules.

160
00:10:35,659 --> 00:10:37,559
You're all dismissed!

161
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:41,900
Coach, about that...

162
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,800
I'm so disappointed.

163
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:48,660
Coach Zhang,

164
00:10:50,930 --> 00:10:53,559
this place isn't safe after all.

165
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:57,020
There's an obvious loophole in the system. Your surveillance cameras didn't catch me.

166
00:10:57,020 --> 00:10:57,840
- If I'm a bad guy...
- Shut up!

167
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:02,539
We'll deal with you later. Your dad will make you pay for this.

168
00:11:02,539 --> 00:11:04,139
Coach,

169
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:07,740
I brought Gao Yang in here. This has nothing to do with them.

170
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:10,939
If you're going to dismiss someone, just dismiss me.

171
00:11:10,939 --> 00:11:12,200
What are you talking about?

172
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,699
Coach, we all knew that Gao Yang is sleeping over.

173
00:11:14,699 --> 00:11:16,519
If you're going to dismiss someone, dismiss us all.

174
00:11:16,519 --> 00:11:18,159
- That's right.
- That's right.
- That's right. Dismiss us all.

175
00:11:18,159 --> 00:11:21,100
Shut up, all of you! Do you think I wouldn't do it?

176
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:23,420
Say no more.

177
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:25,219
Coach,

178
00:11:27,650 --> 00:11:29,259
I'll leave.

179
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:33,679
No, Xiaowen.

180
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:36,239
Coach, please don't be angry.

181
00:11:38,650 --> 00:11:40,440
- Coach.
- Coach. Coach.

182
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,759
- Coach, that's not necessary.
- That's not necessary.

183
00:11:41,759 --> 00:11:44,200
Let me tell you. I'm more experienced than you in something like this.

184
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,020
Just write up a self-criticism, understand?

185
00:11:46,020 --> 00:11:50,060
It's not a big deal, right? Stop packing up.

186
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:52,859
No, Xiaowen. Wait. Why are you so stubborn?

187
00:11:52,859 --> 00:11:57,079
Just plead with that Coach Zhang and admit your wrongdoings, and you'll be okay. Right?

188
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,800
I deserved to be punished for my mistake.

189
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:03,419
I told you I can sleep in an internet café. You just wouldn't listen.

190
00:12:03,419 --> 00:12:06,100
You had to make me stay at your dorm. Look at what happened now.

191
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:09,219
X-Xiaowen, you're leaving?

192
00:12:09,939 --> 00:12:12,579
Stay and focus on your training. Don't worry about me.

193
00:12:12,579 --> 00:12:15,919
B-B-But it was not easy for you to get such an opportunity.

194
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:20,220
- L-L-L-Let's go p-plead w-with the coach again.
- Exactly.

195
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:22,379
Xiaowen,

196
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:26,319
must you leave? If you insist on leaving, we'll leave with you.

197
00:12:26,319 --> 00:12:28,100
This has nothing to do with you.

198
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:31,160
You and I haven't competed yet. Who's letting you leave?

199
00:12:32,179 --> 00:12:34,779
Wait, are you going to give up half way every time?

200
00:12:34,779 --> 00:12:37,079
Rules are rules.

201
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,700
- He... Why is he so stubborn?
- Hurry.

202
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:43,960
No, Xiaowen, there are so many of us here. Look at them,

203
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,900
this matter will escalate, you know?

204
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:47,080
- That way, none of us can train anymore.
- This...

205
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,580
Xiaowen!

206
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:56,339
Coach Zhang, please give Xiaowen another chance.

207
00:12:56,339 --> 00:12:58,040
Xiaowen,

208
00:12:58,040 --> 00:13:01,779
I would normally punish you to run 10,000 meters for what happened today.

209
00:13:01,779 --> 00:13:05,299
However, first of all, I stressed implementing strict discipline.

210
00:13:05,299 --> 00:13:07,940
Secondly, I let you in at the last minute.

211
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:09,819
The other athletes are not happy with that.

212
00:13:09,819 --> 00:13:12,920
That's why I must hold you to a higher standard.

213
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:14,979
Can you understand my dilemma?

214
00:13:14,979 --> 00:13:17,020
I do understand, Coach.

215
00:13:17,020 --> 00:13:21,380
Brother Bin is right. You are an outstanding athlete.

216
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:24,539
There are not many days left of boot camp. Go home and train with Brother Bin.

217
00:13:24,539 --> 00:13:28,779
He's definitely a first-rate coach if he puts his mind to it.

218
00:13:32,860 --> 00:13:36,300
This is your training uniform. It just arrived today.

219
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,840
Keep it as a souvenir.

220
00:13:54,650 --> 00:13:56,659
Coach,

221
00:13:56,659 --> 00:13:58,420
thank you.

222
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:01,440
Alright, stay safe on your way home.

223
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:08,720
Coach,

224
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,420
I'll see you at the national competition.

225
00:14:12,100 --> 00:14:15,239
You're a man of integrity. I'll see you then.

226
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:19,999
Xiaowen, it's all right. Let Brother Bin coach you.

227
00:14:19,999 --> 00:14:22,240
He won't be necessarily worse than him.

228
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:24,179
Xiaowen,

229
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:27,400
you have to get to the finish line next time!

230
00:15:02,770 --> 00:15:06,080
Jin Doudou, what are you doing? I'm studying!

231
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:08,500
I don't see you writing anything down!

232
00:15:08,500 --> 00:15:09,879
Get out!

233
00:15:09,879 --> 00:15:11,539
Sis, let's dance together!

234
00:15:11,539 --> 00:15:13,620
Get off of my bed!

235
00:15:13,620 --> 00:15:16,300
What are you two doing this early in the morning?

236
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:26,180
Are we there yet?

237
00:15:26,180 --> 00:15:27,779
Why are you rushing me?

238
00:15:27,779 --> 00:15:31,140
If you didn't go to the restroom, would we be in such a rush?

239
00:15:31,140 --> 00:15:35,440
Wait, you can't blame me for that. Nature was calling.

240
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:37,459
There aren't restrooms on the train?

241
00:15:37,459 --> 00:15:38,939
Hurry up.

242
00:15:38,939 --> 00:15:40,420
What are our seat numbers again?

243
00:15:40,420 --> 00:15:43,860
- 88, 89.
- 88, 89.

244
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,260
Over here.

245
00:15:51,039 --> 00:15:54,140
Sir, you're in the wrong seat.

246
00:15:54,140 --> 00:15:57,060
No way. This is my seat.

247
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:59,659
Compartment 8 No. 88 and 89.

248
00:15:59,659 --> 00:16:01,600
These are our seats.

249
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,699
I have a ticket too. I'll show you.

250
00:16:03,699 --> 00:16:07,179
That won't work even if you have a ticket. How can you take up two seats?

251
00:16:07,179 --> 00:16:10,020
Look at my physique. How will I fit if I don't buy two seats?

252
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,720
I'll show you my tickets.

253
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,759
See? I have my tickets right here.

254
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,159
Look.

255
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,560
Am I right?

256
00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:21,999
Sir,

257
00:16:21,999 --> 00:16:23,500
you took the opposite train.

258
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:25,380
This train is heading toward Tieyuan.

259
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:29,659
That's not possible. Attendant! Attendant! Is this train heading toward Tieyuan?

260
00:16:29,659 --> 00:16:33,019
No, it came from Tieyuan.

261
00:16:33,019 --> 00:16:35,340
You two took the wrong train.

262
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:39,879
Jin Beibei,

263
00:16:39,879 --> 00:16:43,045
why are you yelling instead of studying so early in the morning?

264
00:16:43,045 --> 00:16:45,959
He's playing music. How can I study?

265
00:16:45,959 --> 00:16:48,379
Doudou is on summer vacation.

266
00:16:48,379 --> 00:16:50,620
So am I!

267
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:53,819
He's an elementary school student. You're a high school student.

268
00:16:53,819 --> 00:16:55,740
Do high school students have summer vacations?

269
00:16:55,740 --> 00:17:00,900
Besides, with your score on the finals, are you entitled to a summer vacation?

270
00:17:00,900 --> 00:17:03,579
He's playing music so loud. How can I do my homework?

271
00:17:03,579 --> 00:17:07,319
Did you write a word when he wasn't playing music?

272
00:17:08,219 --> 00:17:10,240
You're just biased.

273
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,880
Doudou,

274
00:17:16,219 --> 00:17:18,470
let's go get ice-cream.

275
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:21,940
Let your sister study alone quietly.

276
00:17:23,140 --> 00:17:24,840
Where are you going?

277
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:27,259
You're so biased!

278
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:35,979
Sir, you're such a nice person. You're wonderful.

279
00:17:35,979 --> 00:17:37,820
- Where are you from?
- Harbin.

280
00:17:37,820 --> 00:17:39,920
Harbin?

281
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,839
The red sausage there is delicious, right?

282
00:17:41,839 --> 00:17:45,019
Not just red sausage, the dried sausage and pork belly sausage are all delicious.

283
00:17:45,019 --> 00:17:46,978
Then I'll go see you in Harbin next time.

284
00:17:46,978 --> 00:17:48,620
I'll certainly arrange for everything.

285
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:51,680
How hospitable! Next time, when you come to Tieyuan. I'll make arrangements for you.

286
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:53,800
Alright, that's enough.

287
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:56,340
We'll get off at the next station.

288
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:58,100
What else can we do?

289
00:17:58,100 --> 00:18:00,419
Look at you, didn't you get on the wrong train too?

290
00:18:00,419 --> 00:18:02,340
If you didn't insist on going to the restroom there,

291
00:18:02,340 --> 00:18:04,739
would we be in such a hurry? If we weren't in such a hurry, would we get on the wrong train?

292
00:18:04,739 --> 00:18:07,200
If you put it that way, you insisted on me staying in your dorm.

293
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:09,880
- If you didn't do that, would you be dismissed?
- If you didn't make a mistake with the train ticket,

294
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,978
would you be staying overnight?

295
00:18:10,978 --> 00:18:12,179
What are you fighting for?

296
00:18:12,179 --> 00:18:15,780
We're all buddies when we're away from home. Don't fight. Here, give him a tasty treat. Here.

297
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:16,900
Exactly.

298
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:20,060
Here, have some peanuts.

299
00:18:20,060 --> 00:18:21,800
Where are you going?

300
00:18:22,410 --> 00:18:24,559
To the restroom.

301
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:28,999
He's finally gone. It's much roomier now. Come on, move out a little.

302
00:18:28,999 --> 00:18:31,222
[Jenny's Salon]

303
00:18:39,310 --> 00:18:42,939
Beibei, stop crying.

304
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:47,886
You're affecting our business.

305
00:18:49,730 --> 00:18:54,302
My dad is so biased.

306
00:18:54,302 --> 00:18:58,559
It's not the first time you've been treated unfairly. Why did you have a sudden outburst today?

307
00:18:58,559 --> 00:19:01,939
It's about to be the eighth!

308
00:19:01,939 --> 00:19:03,100
What about the eighth?

309
00:19:03,100 --> 00:19:05,540
What do you think?

310
00:19:07,450 --> 00:19:09,359
The eighth...

311
00:19:10,860 --> 00:19:12,959
The eighth is Monday.

312
00:19:12,959 --> 00:19:16,039
Stop talking to me!

313
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:20,380
Men are all heartless!

314
00:19:22,359 --> 00:19:23,200
Do you want a soda?

315
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:25,140
No!

316
00:19:25,970 --> 00:19:29,382
Do what you want then. Stay here by yourself. I'm leaving.

317
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:55,277
Mom, did you touch the stuff in my drawer?

318
00:19:55,277 --> 00:19:56,699
What is it?

319
00:19:56,699 --> 00:19:59,319
A long, transparent box with a bow on top.

320
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:00,319
I didn't see it.

321
00:20:03,122 --> 00:20:07,659
[Jiqing Station]

322
00:20:07,659 --> 00:20:09,839
Jiqing welcomes you.

323
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:15,499
Xiaowen, have you been here before?

324
00:20:16,759 --> 00:20:19,739
Well, it's my first time here. Why don't we walk around?

325
00:20:19,739 --> 00:20:21,620
No, let's hurry up and buy the return tickets.

326
00:20:21,620 --> 00:20:26,952
But it was such a long ride and we didn't have any fun at all. Let's just hang out for a little while before leaving.

327
00:20:26,952 --> 00:20:29,039
I don't want to hang out here.

328
00:20:29,039 --> 00:20:30,879
You're such a downer.

329
00:20:30,879 --> 00:20:32,460
Come on, let's get some food first.

330
00:20:34,010 --> 00:20:36,420
What should we eat?

331
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:40,480
Nobody remembered my birthday.

332
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:42,900
Zhao Jiabao doesn't remember either.

333
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:45,820
Gao Yang won't remember for sure.

334
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:50,079
Men are indeed unreliable.

335
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:59,540
Auntie, I would like to use your phone.

336
00:20:59,540 --> 00:21:01,060
Alright, go on. It's inside.

337
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:03,119
Thank you, Auntie.

338
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:20,900
Hello, Auntie. I'm looking for Tian Meng.

339
00:21:20,900 --> 00:21:22,459
You want to ask her to hang out again?

340
00:21:22,459 --> 00:21:24,480
No, no, I'm not asking her to hang out.

341
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:26,606
I... I want to ask her about a problem.

342
00:21:26,606 --> 00:21:29,179
Alright, wait a moment.

343
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,140
Hello, Beibei.

344
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:34,840
Meng, I...

345
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,259
Have you finished your homework?

346
00:21:36,259 --> 00:21:41,939
Not yet. I just wanted to ask. That... do you have any plans on the eighth?

347
00:21:41,939 --> 00:21:44,739
I don't have any plans. I'll still be grounded.

348
00:21:44,739 --> 00:21:49,780
No, think about it, the eighth is a special day.

349
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:52,219
Can you remember?

350
00:21:52,219 --> 00:21:55,444
Oh, I remember.

351
00:21:55,444 --> 00:21:56,440
Thank you for reminding me.

352
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:58,900
That's okay! We're besties!

353
00:21:58,900 --> 00:22:02,319
The magazine I submitted to will publish an issue on the 8th.

354
00:22:02,319 --> 00:22:03,340
I have to check it.

355
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:04,440
Why don't you think again?

356
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:06,340
My mom's glaring at me. Bye.

357
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:08,319
Hello? Hello? No...

358
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:17,859
Zhao Jiabao, I'm thirsty.

359
00:22:17,859 --> 00:22:20,440
Go... go get yourself some water.

360
00:22:20,440 --> 00:22:22,799
What kind of person is that?

361
00:22:30,210 --> 00:22:33,320
The number you've dialed is overdue.

362
00:22:33,320 --> 00:22:37,140
The number you've dialed is over... overdue.

363
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:40,800
The number you've dialed is overdue.

364
00:22:43,490 --> 00:22:47,380
The number you've dialed is overdue.

365
00:22:48,340 --> 00:22:51,419
That's not right. This is the right number.

366
00:22:51,419 --> 00:22:53,819
Mi Daqiang, is that you?

367
00:22:53,819 --> 00:22:55,300
No, it's not me!

368
00:22:55,300 --> 00:22:57,700
Hello? Hello?

369
00:23:04,340 --> 00:23:05,259
Gao Yang!

370
00:23:05,259 --> 00:23:08,179
Hello, Brother Bin. What's up?

371
00:23:08,179 --> 00:23:11,319
Coach Zhang called me. What did you do this time?

372
00:23:11,319 --> 00:23:12,620
Don't be anxious.

373
00:23:12,620 --> 00:23:16,320
See how I will deal with you when you get back. Where are you guys now?

374
00:23:16,320 --> 00:23:20,040
We are... in Jiqing.
[Jiqing Station]

375
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:22,240
We took the wrong train.

376
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:25,919
Jiqing? Why are you in Xiaowen's hometown?

377
00:23:26,219 --> 00:23:28,759
- This is Xiaowen's hometown?
- Yes.

378
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:32,259
You just won't stop causing trouble for me. Put Xiaowen on the phone.

379
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:34,160
Xiaowen,
[Jiqing Station]

380
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,160
it's Brother Bin.

381
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,580
Hello, Mr. Gao.

382
00:23:39,580 --> 00:23:44,019
Xiaowen, don't worry about your training. We'll talk about it when you come back.

383
00:23:44,019 --> 00:23:47,459
Why did you go back to your hometown? Are you homesick?

384
00:23:47,459 --> 00:23:50,420
No, we took the wrong train.

385
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:52,259
That's okay.

386
00:23:52,259 --> 00:23:55,219
Just go take a good look around. You don't go home very often.

387
00:23:55,219 --> 00:23:59,280
No. We're buying tickets and going back now. Don't worry.

388
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:00,689
Alright, alright.

389
00:24:00,689 --> 00:24:02,389
Xiaowen,

390
00:24:02,389 --> 00:24:04,939
keep an eye on Gao Yang for me. Don't let him run about.

391
00:24:04,939 --> 00:24:08,707
Okay.
[Jiqing Station]

392
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,700
Gao Yang!

393
00:24:21,920 --> 00:24:23,620
Gao Yang!

394
00:24:25,219 --> 00:24:29,919
Jiqing is a city built upon oil fields.

395
00:24:29,919 --> 00:24:32,140
It's located in the north of our country.
[One Day Tour of Jiqing]

396
00:24:32,140 --> 00:24:35,060
The city has a long history and glorious traditions.

397
00:24:35,060 --> 00:24:38,879
Jiqing is a city built upon oil fields.

398
00:24:38,879 --> 00:24:40,659
It's located in the north of our country.

399
00:24:40,659 --> 00:24:44,259
The city has a long history and glorious traditions.

400
00:24:44,259 --> 00:24:48,700
My mom and dad are both honorable petroleum engineers.

401
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:53,259
My dream for the future is to study hard, make progress every day,

402
00:24:53,259 --> 00:24:57,819
get into the Beijing University of Technology, and serve the country just like them.

403
00:24:57,819 --> 00:24:59,160
Xiaowen recited it very nicely.

404
00:24:59,160 --> 00:25:00,499
Ye Xiaowen!

405
00:25:00,499 --> 00:25:03,000
...is a city built upon oil fields.

406
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:05,839
- Over here! Over here! Let's go get some food!
 - It's located in the north of our country.

407
00:25:05,839 --> 00:25:09,499
The city has a long history and glorious traditions.

408
00:25:13,939 --> 00:25:16,219
Xiaowen, I've looked into it.

409
00:25:16,219 --> 00:25:18,739
The restaurants at the train station are tourist traps.

410
00:25:18,739 --> 00:25:22,100
It's unpalatable and expensive. Let's go eat in the city, okay?

411
00:25:22,100 --> 00:25:25,259
It'll be cheaper. We mustn't waste that kind of money.

412
00:25:25,259 --> 00:25:27,459
Taking a cab isn't a waste of money?

413
00:25:27,459 --> 00:25:31,340
I already negotiated with the driver. A fixed price of 5 Yuan, right?

414
00:25:31,340 --> 00:25:32,799
Yes, yes.

415
00:25:32,799 --> 00:25:33,979
5 Yuan.

416
00:25:33,979 --> 00:25:36,659
See, the driver is so nice. Right?

417
00:25:36,659 --> 00:25:41,659
Sir, take us to the most delicious and unique old restaurant in Jiqing.

418
00:25:41,659 --> 00:25:43,100
Okay.

419
00:25:43,100 --> 00:25:46,580
Let's go home after we eat. Don't make Mr. Gao worry.

420
00:25:46,580 --> 00:25:48,380
I know, I know.

421
00:26:27,322 --> 00:26:30,277
[Happy birthday to Jin Beibei]

422
00:26:30,277 --> 00:26:38,762
[Hope these headphones will improve your taste!!!]

423
00:26:45,722 --> 00:26:50,442
[The best composer, Zhao Jiabao]

424
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:57,099
Xiaowen, what do you think?

425
00:26:57,099 --> 00:26:59,899
We've visited so many places. Which place do you like the best?

426
00:27:05,730 --> 00:27:08,599
They are all the same. I don't feel anything.

427
00:27:08,599 --> 00:27:10,399
They're all the same?

428
00:27:11,380 --> 00:27:13,840
Here are your colorful tossed clear noodles.

429
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:16,759
Try this. This is a Jiqing specialty dish.

430
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:28,080
How is it?

431
00:27:28,868 --> 00:27:30,060
It's okay.

432
00:27:30,060 --> 00:27:33,000
Nothing special?

433
00:27:37,730 --> 00:27:39,340
Boss. Come here for a moment, Boss.

434
00:27:39,340 --> 00:27:41,140
Coming.

435
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:42,839
What's wrong, Bro?

436
00:27:42,839 --> 00:27:44,780
Wait, is this a Jiqing specialty?

437
00:27:44,780 --> 00:27:46,820
Yes, we've been in business for a dozen years.

438
00:27:46,820 --> 00:27:48,140
How many years exactly?

439
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:49,699
About ten years.

440
00:27:49,699 --> 00:27:52,079
That won't do. Your restaurant hasn't been opened long enough.

441
00:27:52,079 --> 00:27:55,419
Is there any restaurant that has been open for a really long time

442
00:27:55,419 --> 00:27:57,340
and everyone in Jiqing ate there before?

443
00:27:57,340 --> 00:27:58,780
Where can I find that for you?

444
00:27:58,780 --> 00:28:00,959
Wait, just think about it, Boss.

445
00:28:00,959 --> 00:28:03,140
My friend rarely has a chance to come back to Jiqing.

446
00:28:03,140 --> 00:28:06,000
He just wants to find the taste of his childhood.

447
00:28:06,699 --> 00:28:09,459
Xiaowen, why did you leave? Where are you going?

448
00:28:09,459 --> 00:28:10,620
Back to the train station.

449
00:28:10,620 --> 00:28:13,320
Let's walk around for a bit longer. If this restaurant doesn't taste good, we'll find another one.

450
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:16,219
Gao Yang, I know what you're doing. I don't need it.

451
00:28:16,219 --> 00:28:17,499
Wait, what's wrong?

452
00:28:17,499 --> 00:28:21,599
I know you mean well. You want me to take a good look at Jiqing.

453
00:28:23,170 --> 00:28:26,319
But I'm telling you, I don't remember this place at all.

454
00:28:26,780 --> 00:28:27,900
Not at all?

455
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:29,500
No.

456
00:28:30,060 --> 00:28:32,399
I can't remember anything.

457
00:28:34,219 --> 00:28:36,839
The streets here look very unfamiliar,

458
00:28:36,839 --> 00:28:41,599
and the food doesn't have the same taste as before. This place has nothing to do with me.

459
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,519
But this is your hometown.

460
00:28:43,519 --> 00:28:45,979
It's not if I don't remember.

461
00:28:45,979 --> 00:28:48,760
No, Xiaowen, maybe... let's go visit your old family house.

462
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:50,460
I'm not going!

463
00:28:51,060 --> 00:28:54,399
- But why?
- No reason! I said I'm not going, so I won't go!

464
00:28:56,140 --> 00:28:58,499
Don't you miss your parents?

465
00:28:58,499 --> 00:29:00,820
My parents are already dead.

466
00:29:09,499 --> 00:29:12,440
That's just an empty house.

467
00:29:19,860 --> 00:29:22,459
What would change if I go there?

468
00:29:24,970 --> 00:29:27,259
What would happen if I visit it?

469
00:29:30,410 --> 00:29:32,680
Can I go back in time?

470
00:29:34,100 --> 00:29:36,079
I just don't want...

471
00:29:36,599 --> 00:29:38,979
you to have regrets.

472
00:29:40,519 --> 00:29:45,539
Maybe you can find some old photos there

473
00:29:45,539 --> 00:29:47,979
and save them for a keepsake or something.

474
00:29:48,620 --> 00:29:50,979
I do miss them very much,

475
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:59,520
but I don't want to be stuck in the past.

476
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:05,419
Let's go back to Tieyuan.

477
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:17,659
That's enough.

478
00:30:17,659 --> 00:30:21,140
Go home and apologize to your dad and we can put this behind us.

479
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:25,259
Why should I apologize? He was clearly biased.

480
00:30:25,259 --> 00:30:27,659
Doudou is younger than you, right?

481
00:30:27,659 --> 00:30:29,140
Well...

482
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:30,659
you're biased too!

483
00:30:30,659 --> 00:30:32,960
How am I biased?

484
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:37,019
Isn't Doudou younger than her? You're calling me biased?

485
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:40,939
Your dad didn't do anything besides spend time with you all summer vacation.

486
00:30:40,939 --> 00:30:44,179
Aren't I here to look for you, too? What? Your parents still don't love you enough?

487
00:30:44,179 --> 00:30:46,819
- What else do you want?
- Come on, don't move.

488
00:30:46,819 --> 00:30:49,159
This child. I must say...

489
00:30:49,159 --> 00:30:52,700
Beibei, look at how nice your parents are towards you.

490
00:30:52,700 --> 00:30:56,000
If my Jiabao runs away, I'm not going to look for him.

491
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:58,080
- Did you hear that?
- I'll treat it as saving money on food.

492
00:30:58,080 --> 00:31:00,079
She's still not satisfied.

493
00:31:00,599 --> 00:31:03,380
- Do you know what's wrong with her?
- What is it?

494
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:06,720
Someone's birthday is coming up.

495
00:31:10,099 --> 00:31:11,780
Then does my dad know?

496
00:31:11,780 --> 00:31:13,780
Yes, he does.

497
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:15,019
He even bought you a gift.

498
00:31:15,019 --> 00:31:16,019
What did he buy?

499
00:31:16,019 --> 00:31:17,619
He bought you a...

500
00:31:17,619 --> 00:31:20,029
- He won't let me tell you.
- Beibei!

501
00:31:20,029 --> 00:31:22,159
- Auntie.
- Jiabao, you really scared me. You're home?

502
00:31:22,159 --> 00:31:23,679
Hello, Auntie.

503
00:31:23,679 --> 00:31:24,860
Beibei, come here for a moment.

504
00:31:24,860 --> 00:31:26,499
Wait a minute. I need to talk to my mom for a while.

505
00:31:26,499 --> 00:31:28,200
Reveal a bit about it to me, Mom.

506
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:31,940
Your dad won't let me tell you. Don't let it slip when you go home. Do you hear me?

507
00:31:32,340 --> 00:31:35,499
Then I want a boombox, the type that's louder than Doudou's.

508
00:31:35,499 --> 00:31:38,939
What boombox? Your dad hates loud noises. You know that.

509
00:31:38,939 --> 00:31:41,679
If you want to listen to music, put on headphones. Do you hear me?

510
00:31:41,679 --> 00:31:43,739
I don't want to put on headphones.

511
00:31:43,739 --> 00:31:46,540
I don't like headphones. They make my ears hurt.

512
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:48,799
Wearing headphones make your ears hurt? What do you want?

513
00:31:48,799 --> 00:31:50,680
Look at how picky kids are these days.

514
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:52,939
Let's go inside. Why do you want to see me?

515
00:31:52,939 --> 00:31:56,340
- Look at her!
- Well, Jiabao is the same way.

516
00:31:56,340 --> 00:31:57,419
They really make you worry about them.

517
00:31:57,419 --> 00:31:59,780
Why do you want to talk to me?

518
00:32:00,659 --> 00:32:03,359
Aren't you thirsty? I'll pour you some water.

519
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:06,880
You have a conscience after all. It's so hard to get some water at your house.

520
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:08,280
Here.

521
00:32:09,739 --> 00:32:13,820
Well, you really don't like headphones, Beibei?

522
00:32:15,820 --> 00:32:18,500
They make my ears hurt after I wear them for a while.

523
00:32:19,300 --> 00:32:22,801
That's true. They make my ears hurt too when I wear them for a long time.

524
00:32:22,801 --> 00:32:24,420
That's right.

525
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:30,979
What would he gift me then?

526
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:52,860
- Did you come to Jiqing to travel?
- Yes.

527
00:32:53,659 --> 00:32:55,499
Where are you guys from?

528
00:32:55,499 --> 00:32:57,280
Jiqing.

529
00:32:58,540 --> 00:33:01,459
I am. He's not.

530
00:33:01,459 --> 00:33:03,299
Where do you live?

531
00:33:04,730 --> 00:33:06,039
The Oil Field Living Quarters.

532
00:33:06,039 --> 00:33:10,059
I'm familiar with that place. Compound 1? Compound 2?

533
00:33:11,340 --> 00:33:12,939
Compound 2.

534
00:33:13,499 --> 00:33:16,979
They are about to tear it down soon. No one is living there anymore.

535
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,620
When are they tearing it down, Sir?

536
00:33:19,620 --> 00:33:22,800
At the end of next month they will demolish it.

537
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:32,160
Sir, is it far from here?

538
00:33:32,160 --> 00:33:35,860
No. Make a right turn up ahead and it's about a few hundred meters away.

539
00:33:43,530 --> 00:33:44,640
Why did he leave?

540
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,979
Gao Yang!

541
00:33:45,979 --> 00:33:47,579
Gao Yang!

542
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,620
Slow down!

543
00:33:50,620 --> 00:33:52,920
Gao Yang, where are you going?

544
00:33:56,490 --> 00:33:57,580
Gao Yang, stop running!

545
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:59,539
I just want to go and take a look!

546
00:33:59,539 --> 00:34:00,459
Come back!

547
00:34:00,459 --> 00:34:02,499
I'll just take one look!

548
00:34:04,730 --> 00:34:05,499
Do you want to die?

549
00:34:05,499 --> 00:34:07,499
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

550
00:34:07,499 --> 00:34:10,899
Gao Yang! Be careful!

551
00:34:13,180 --> 00:34:15,660
There's money in the backpack! There's money in the backpack!

552
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:32,800
Auntie, how... how do I get to Compound 2 of the Oil Field Living Quarters?

553
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:35,159
- Make a left at the intersection up ahead.
- Thank you.

554
00:34:35,159 --> 00:34:36,939
Gao Yang!

555
00:34:45,242 --> 00:34:46,882
[Compound 2 of Oil Field Living Quarters]

556
00:34:51,380 --> 00:34:52,579
Uncle.

557
00:34:52,579 --> 00:34:54,379
Uncle.

558
00:34:54,379 --> 00:34:55,380
What do you want?

559
00:34:55,380 --> 00:34:57,759
Please let me in to have a look.

560
00:34:57,759 --> 00:35:00,459
Why do you want to come inside? Everyone already moved out.

561
00:35:00,459 --> 00:35:02,600
They're tearing it down soon.

562
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:05,660
I... I... I used to live here.

563
00:35:05,660 --> 00:35:07,019
That's not possible.

564
00:35:07,019 --> 00:35:10,139
I know everyone around here. Why haven't I seen you before?

565
00:35:10,139 --> 00:35:12,839
I... Look at me, Uncle.

566
00:35:12,839 --> 00:35:15,059
I'm Xiaowen. I'm from the Ye Family.

567
00:35:15,059 --> 00:35:17,619
You're Ye Xiaowen?

568
00:35:18,559 --> 00:35:21,600
You've really grown up! Alright, alright. Come in.

569
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:24,020
- Thank you, Uncle.
- Come in and take a look.

570
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:26,119
Really!

571
00:35:28,490 --> 00:35:32,619
Uncle. Uncle, which apartment did I live in?

572
00:35:32,619 --> 00:35:35,939
You moved away for so long that you forgot your own home?

573
00:35:35,939 --> 00:35:38,780
Building 3, Room 201.

574
00:35:38,780 --> 00:35:41,021
Thank you. Thank you.

575
00:35:56,610 --> 00:35:59,680
Xiaowen, what are you drawing?

576
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:03,260
I'm drawing Daddy, Mommy, and me.

577
00:36:03,260 --> 00:36:04,820
Xiaowen is such a good boy.

578
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:05,700
Xiaowen,

579
00:36:05,700 --> 00:36:08,900
if you ever get separated from me, look for this drawing.

580
00:36:08,900 --> 00:36:11,660
If you find this drawing, it means you're not far from home.

581
00:36:11,660 --> 00:36:14,299
But I don't want to get separated from you.

582
00:36:14,299 --> 00:36:18,200
Silly child, I'm saying just in case.

583
00:36:20,700 --> 00:36:23,819
Xiaowen, what else do you want to eat?

584
00:36:24,180 --> 00:36:25,340
Tossed clear noodles.

585
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:27,980
Tossed clear noodles?

586
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:30,659
All right, Daddy will take you to eat some tossed clear noodles.

587
00:36:30,659 --> 00:36:32,299
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

588
00:36:32,299 --> 00:36:34,879
Come on, finish your cotton candy first.

589
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,919
Cotton candy is your favorite.

590
00:36:45,860 --> 00:36:51,059
Mommy, hurry. Mommy, ride faster. Daddy, hurry and catch up!

591
00:36:51,059 --> 00:36:52,460
Then hold on tightly.

592
00:36:52,460 --> 00:36:54,220
I know.

593
00:36:54,220 --> 00:36:58,180
Slow down, Son. Wait for Daddy!

594
00:36:58,740 --> 00:36:59,979
Slow down, Baby.

595
00:36:59,979 --> 00:37:02,079
Hurry up!

596
00:37:24,042 --> 00:37:26,562
[Jiqing Station]

597
00:37:46,922 --> 00:37:52,970
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

598
00:37:52,970 --> 00:38:00,135
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

599
00:38:00,135 --> 00:38:06,225
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

600
00:38:06,225 --> 00:38:12,265
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

601
00:38:12,265 --> 00:38:18,817
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

602
00:38:18,817 --> 00:38:24,457
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

603
00:38:24,457 --> 00:38:28,470
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

604
00:38:28,470 --> 00:38:31,892
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

605
00:38:31,892 --> 00:38:35,187
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

606
00:38:35,187 --> 00:38:41,947
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

607
00:38:41,947 --> 00:38:45,158
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

608
00:38:45,158 --> 00:38:49,370
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

609
00:38:49,370 --> 00:38:53,090
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

610
00:38:53,090 --> 00:39:00,950
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
